Privacy Policy
Last modified: Aug. 19, 2018
Your privacy is important to us. When you use the Infinity Insight Developer’s Mobile applications (the "App") you are subject to this privacy policy (the "Privacy Policy"). Sometimes we need information to provide services that you request. This Privacy Policy describes the information collected by Infinity Insight Developer through our mobile applications and how we use that information. We are committed to protecting the privacy of all visitors, Users and others who access our application (“you,” or “Users”).
Our Privacy Policy Explains:
§  What information we collect and why we collect it.
§  How we use that information.
§  The choices we offer, including how to access and update information.
§  If you do not agree with this policy, do not use our App or provide Infinity Insight Developer with your information.
General
Users can access the App through our Applications on Devices. A “Device” is any computer used to access the App, including without limitation a desktop, laptop, mobile phone, tablet, or other consumer electronic device. This Privacy Policy governs your access to the App, regardless of how you access it. By using our App you consent to the collection, transfer, processing, storage, disclosure and other uses described in this Privacy Policy.
Children's Privacy
We acknowledge the importance in protecting the privacy of children when collecting their Personal Information through our APP. Please note that children can choose whether to share their information with us, and we will not require a child to provide more information than is reasonably necessary in order to participate in the APP's activities. We encourage parents to assist us in making their children's information secure, by instructing their children to provide their personal information upon their parental permission.
When we collect the Personal Information of children, we take the necessary steps to assure the protection of their information by;
Limiting the collection of children's Personal Information to the extent necessary to provide them with the required services.
We will not transfer Children's Personal Information for any reason other than provided in this Privacy Policy.
We will provide access to parents, who wish to review the Personal Information we hold about their children, as well as comply with their request for erasure and rectification of the information, if such is required.
If you are under the age of 18, you should read this Privacy Policy with you parents or legal guardians, and ask questions about the things in this Privacy Policy that you do not understand. If you are under the age of 13, please ask your parents or legal guardian for permission before you provide us with any of your Personal Information.
Collection of Information
Save Image to Your Device Storage
Our apps have feature to save app’s assets such as image to your phone storage those can be use for offline purpose, if you don’t have any internet access or you don’t need to open the app instead. This feature use write local storage permission in our app’s manifest.
Use of Information:
We may use Personal Information submitted by you for the following purposes: Help us develop, deliver, and improve our products and services and supply higher quality service; manage online surveys and other activities you have participated in.
We may further collect and use non-personal information in the following circumstances: to have a better understanding of the User’s behavior, solve problems regarding products and services, improve our products, services and advertising. We may collect and process further anonymized information and data that is not processed by reference to a specific individual.
Your Rights and Data Retention
You can request the deletion of the Personal Information Infinity Insight Developer has collected or withdraw your consent to the processing of such information, and disable its future collection by contacting us at ii.developer19@gmail.com. From that point, we shall not have the right to process your Personal Information, and you'll not be allowed to use our App. Note, however, that you may withdraw consent at any time, without affecting the lawfulness of data processing we carried out based on your consent before such withdrawal.
If you are located within the European Union (the "EU"), you may be entitled with some additional rights. For further information and/or for the exercising of such rights, please contact us at ii.developer19@gmail.com.
Infinity Insight Developer does not retain information longer than required to provide the App and for its reasonable business needs, or for other essential purposes such as complying with our legal obligations, resolving disputes, and enforcing our agreements.
Infinity Insight Developer may at all times review, retain and disclose any other information as Infinity Insight Developer deems necessary to satisfy any applicable law, regulation, legal process or governmental request and Infinity Insight Developer's needs and necessities. By doing so, Infinity Insight Developer does not either expressly or impliedly endorse, affirm or in any manner assume any responsibility for such communications.
Information Security
The security of your Personal Information is important to us, but remember that no method of transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage is 100% secure. While we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your Personal Information, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.
Contact Infinity Insight Developer / Abuse Reports
If you have a privacy concern, complaint, or a question or believe that your privacy has been compromised by any person, in the course of using the App, or any other requests, responses, questions and complaints, then please contact Infinity Insight Developer via ii.developer19@gmail.com.
Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may change this Privacy Policy from time to time, when necessary to reflect customer feedback and changes in our App. When we post changes to this policy, we will revise the "last modified" date at the top of the policy. If we make a change to this Privacy Policy that we believe materially reduces your rights, we will provide a notice prior to the change becoming effective. We encourage you to periodically review this page for the latest information on our privacy practices. We may provide notice of changes in other circumstances as well. By continuing to use the App after those changes become effective, you agree to be bound by the revised Privacy Policy.
